2005-06-10 22:45  rio

	* include/napi.h: Added check for '__APPLE__', since Mac OS X does
	  not automatically define '__unix__'.	This is no longer needed
	  for autoconf, but other applications that use napi.h need to know
	  that Mac OS X is a unix system.

