	  which doesn't work with the XML API.

2005-06-06 10:36  faa59

	* install_nexus_dep_rpm: Script to download and install HDF rpms

2005-06-06 10:07  faa59

	* include/: napi.h, napi4.h: Change headers slightly so that napi.h
	  no longer depends on HDF includes; this should make it easier for
	  people to build applications as they only then need the HDF
	  libraries and not the HDF includes. Only code change was to make
	  iTag and iRef in the NXlink strcuture long rather than int32 - as
	  far as I can tell a reference to these is never passed to a
	  function and so there should be no conflict with the sizeof(long)
	  varying on platforms

