2004-12-07 17:53  jph

	* applications/NXtranslate/IPNS_CPP/: Runfile.cpp, Runfile.h: Add
	  in new methods to Get 1D spectra out of a runfile Get a vector of
	  Segment objects.  This may be used by other function.

	  Also make the input stream a private member of the class.  This
	  helps keep this class alive during runtime.  This may later be
	  made part of RandomAccessRunfile for robustness.

2004-12-07 17:51  jph

	* applications/NXtranslate/IPNS_CPP/: RandomAccessRunfile.cpp,
	  RandomAccessRunfile.h: Add in new methods to seek to a new
	  position in file.  Read data stored as shorts or ints in the file
	  into a vector of floats.

	  Also make the input stream a private member of the class.  This
	  helps keep this class alive during runtime.  This may later be
	  made part of RandomAccessRunfile for robustness.

2004-12-07 17:47  jph

	* applications/NXtranslate/IPNS_CPP/Header.cpp: Add in some missing
	  functions

2004-12-07 08:51  mk

	* bindings/f77/napif.f, bindings/f77/napif.inc,
	  bindings/java/native/NexusFile.c,
	  bindings/java/native/neutron_nexus_NexusFile.h,
	  bindings/java/neutron/nexus/NeXusFileInterface.java,
	  bindings/java/neutron/nexus/NexusFile.java,
	  bindings/swig/Makefile, bindings/swig/nxinter.i,
	  bindings/swig/nxinterhelper.c, bindings/swig/nxinterhelper.h,
	  include/napi.h, src/napi.c: - Added NXopengrouppath which opens
	  the group below a path denoting   a dataset. If the terminal
	  symbol of the path is a group,   NXopengrouppath ends in that
	  group.  - Added NXopensourcepath which opens the group from which
	  a dataset was   linked. Pleae note that this only works with
	  files which were written with   the NeXus 3.0 API. Only those
	  contain the necessary target attribute to   linked datasets.	-
	  Added NX_BINARY and NX_BOOLEAN

