	* configure.ac, src/Makefile.am, test/Makefile.am,
	  test/napi_test.c, test/testsuite.at: Add XML interface into
	  autotools and test suite.

	  The build works OK except for a missing stptok() function - I
	  found a free implementation on the internet but haven't included
	  it in case Mark has a better version which he can add to CVS.

	  The testsuite builds, but the tests currently fail.

