	  xml_parser.cpp: Upgraded debuging system. The three levels of
	  debugging are better defined.

2004-12-01 16:51  pfp

	* applications/NXtranslate/xml_parser.cpp: Changed program logic to
	  reflect practices in xml based NeXus files. If there is a name
	  attribute the type is the tag, if there is a type attribute the
	  name is the tag, if neither are defined it has the type NX_CHAR.

