2004-06-03 10:20  faa

	* bindings/f90/Makefile.am: Fix make install problem for F90 shared
	  libraries on Darwin. During the install the libraries need to be
	  relinked, but the relink command written to libNeXus90.la by
	  libtool does not have the correct "tag".  I've added a new target
	  to "all" that does a quick edit of libNeXus90.la after the build
	  to fix the relink

