2004-05-28 13:52  rio

	* bindings/f90/NXUmodule.f90: Added new constant-size arrays
	  (data_shape) to contain the SHAPE of the read data.  The XLF
	  compiler will not allow assumed-size arrays as the SHAPE argument
	  in the RESHAPE intrinsic.

