2004-05-03 12:26  jk

	* autogen.sh: Improve the build of the configur script. It tries to
	  find the newest version of autoconf, automake, and libtool. At
	  least it needs the following versions:

		  autoconf	  2.52
		  automake	  1.5.X
		  libtool	  1.4.2

	  It was tested on a clean RedHat system 7.3 without any additional
	  installed software.

