2004-02-23 20:28  faa

	* configure.ac: Add in -single_module command for darwin linking

2004-02-23 19:45  faa

	* release/: nexus-2.0.0-1.i386.rpm, nexus-2.0.0-1.src.rpm: Add in
	  test NeXus RPMs - they are currently HDF4 / F77 only

2004-02-23 19:35  faa

	* nexus_spec.in: Correct date format on line

2004-02-23 19:23  faa

	* AUTHORS: Update email addresses

2004-02-23 19:11  faa

	* configure.ac: Add test for -fno-common for C compiler flags (i
	  don't think this is a problem on architecture other than MAC);
	  also added a commented out line for the same option for F77. The
	  man page for g77 does not recommend using -fno-common, but i
	  don't believe you will be able to build a shared library on MAC
	  without it. I think it may be used to implement common blocks,
	  which as we don't use we may be able to specify it.

2004-02-23 10:46  faa

	* include/napi5.h, src/napi.c, src/napi5.c: Mangle cacheSize to
	  nx_cacheSize and add extern declaration to the header; I think
	  this should fix it, but I don't actually have an hdf5
	  distribution to test it on

