	* napi.c, src/napi.c: - Renamed napi45.c back to napi.c since this
	  is the main C interface - Added NXACC_CREATE4 to possible open
	  options - eventually, we may	 want to make NXACC_CREATE make
	  HDF5 files by default.

	  Ray

